------Using VIM--------------------------------

curl -O : testing api , ....
vim test.txt => 
(
    : 
    set number 
    syntax on 
    : quit ! 
    h : left 
    l : right 
    j : down 
    k : up 
    w : following word 
    b : previous word 
    0 : beginning of line
    $ : end of line
    8gg : go to line 8
    u : undo 
    cltrl+r : undo 
    o : insert after the line 
    shift + o : insert before the line
    :w : write modification
    :wq : write and quit the program
    G
    d : 
    dd : cut or delete line 
    4dd : delete 4 lines 
    dG : delete all 
    p: paste 
    ----Find and Replace ------
    / :search 
    n :next 
    ctrl +n : previous 
    :%s/to_replace/replacer/gc : replacement with confirmation

    ------ create file ---------------------------
    vim filename.txt 
    vim .vimrc 
)
